    <h1 align> 버튼을 누르면 글자가 사라짐.</h1>
  <form>
    <input type="button" value="버튼1" onclick="back(this.value)"/>
    <input type="button" value="버튼2" onclick="back(this.value)"/>
    <input type="button" value="버튼3" onclick="back(this.value)"/><br/>
